 ?x a dbpedia-owl:MusicalArtist.
 ?x dbpedia-owl:instrument dbpedia:Guitar. 
 ?y a dbpedia-owl:Person.
 ?y a yago:GermanFilmActors.
 ?y foaf:givenName ?ygn.
 ?x dbpedia-owl:abstract ?xabs.
 ?x foaf:surname ?xsurname.
 filter regex(?xabs,concat(?ygn," ",?xsurname) as ?ccat,"i").
 ?y dbpedia-owl:abstract ?yabs
 filter regex(?yabs,"nazi","i").
 filter (langMatches(lang(?xabs), "fr")).
}
